Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在掛麵裡放橘子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡就挑開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺味道都進到湯裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  吃好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去朋友家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.68,0:00:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家一起寫劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要戴頂帽子去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺難為情的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會有難為情的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的影子會很濃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不做  你可成不了女生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.23,0:01:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成年以後要去做手術嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是桃子今天努力烤出來的蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是為你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道刀子和叉子夠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假還這麼認真  真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉同學的媽媽真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  小千要準備切蛋糕了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那份好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你盤子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}都說不是那塊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}小千
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}兩塊比一比厚度完全不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}我看都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  這是二鳥君的份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}我做的很認真的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}把它弄散了才倒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}什麼嘛  那桃子你來弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}還是小千你弄吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}知道了  那我再試一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子果然手藝不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  好歹你也是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒東西要洗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在清洗廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子總愛生氣不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他們兩個會被選中嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅密歐和茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是投票決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要報名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉同學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須投我一票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話什麼意思  威脅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千葉的哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是沙織的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和小沙關係很好的好哥哥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰巧經常去同一所教會而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:05:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  現在在教會裡連你人影都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？也有我的份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥君  拿下叉子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥君…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡穿女裝的二鳥君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女裝是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟你在…恍然大悟個什麼勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才他說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從什麼時候開始的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從小就有的興趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是習慣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥君很為難不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小千
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那個…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我不是存心想讓你為難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你的錯  虧你還一副平心靜氣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才那個人自己發脾氣好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果傷到你的話我向你道歉  二鳥君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是人妖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織喜歡那種類型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟哪裡好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為可愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  我的曲線也不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對比他可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在還記得先給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  入場卷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想叫上麻衣子一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校肯定會引起一片轟動  還是作罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引不起轟動的我  還真是對不住你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  就當是看真穗的男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安那  可別喜歡上他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠君  飯馬上就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天二鳥的姐姐不在  感覺好自在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥  別太在意那件事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更科同學也是男生打扮來上學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在場同學也不會把這事傳出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說錯了？並沒放在心上？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能說完全沒放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（今天辛苦了  劇本感覺挺不錯的）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（下次是星期四對吧  多關照哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡訊裡沒有提到剛才的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為她不會再來幫忙寫劇本了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  二鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我漸漸明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我如此生氣的高槻同學陪伴在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要高槻同學在身邊  我真的會感覺很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然喜歡高槻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並不是只想和她交往的那種喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同學也一定會是那個最瞭解我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用腦過度了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於可以開始練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到最後  只是讓男女角色對換而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這齣羅密歐與茱麗葉一點深度都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻很喜歡這劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是大家努力完成的劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了熱熱鬧鬧地慶祝完工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特意買了煙火來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇形煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不搭嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏日的末尾  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定決心這次不會再留下遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木君抽中了茱麗葉的乳娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是叫奶媽才對哦  佐佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是羅密歐的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具舞會的客人A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}這算什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二學期一開始就決定角色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還用抽籤的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然稅所那傢伙  一點進步都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥店老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幫助羅密歐和茱麗葉的修道士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個是高槻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是修道士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織  再不快點好角色要沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅密歐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了  茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅密歐和茱麗葉  決定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得你特地來接他  真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  麵包拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果見到二鳥  我絕對會把茱麗葉讓給他演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我來  二鳥要適合得多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且對千葉同學也很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭低三下四的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣  你就把茱麗葉讓給二鳥君演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的罪惡感也會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界可不是以千葉同學和二鳥為中心轉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出真話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  世界並沒有以二鳥君為中心轉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把前面一段省去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你討厭  索性讓全世界的人都斷氣不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  殺了他們  讓大家都去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是羅密歐和茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有藥店老闆  修道士  路人A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把登場人物不留一人統統殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰暗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我很陰暗  所以我沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是佐佐也不是你朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐要是聽到了會很傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也把你當作朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼叫得那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  大清早就精神十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釘子敲歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把藍色和黃色混起來不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…重要的公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直尺…直尺在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小誠  給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱麗葉小姐茱麗葉小姐  請您等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再排練下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇本有變動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉來一下行嗎  二鳥也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼事到如今還要改
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我轉念一想再激烈淒慘些會更好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之放學後再慢慢談  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然二鳥君說很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點也不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我們兩個把故事擴展出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻被大家弄得一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點也不喜歡那種台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此如果二鳥演茱麗葉的話 還是很棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣想著才一直忍耐到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小誠他一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙說過要把茱麗葉讓給二鳥君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說過那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  那個人到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是二鳥有那麼一點期待過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點還是有的  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  老實地告訴了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說  我也是很想演茱麗葉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我都想演  即便被大家嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人會嘲笑你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥怎麼會懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  抱怨起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被嘲笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小學裡也被嘲笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我娘娘腔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是高槻同學和小誠理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:17:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才覺得很多事都不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果覺得我不夠理解你  我想去理解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人嘲笑你  我一定會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我只是有些乖僻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把文化祭的票子放著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後台詞還是沒有改吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說稅所老師說服了千葉同學好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說單方面地央求她好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉同學絕對沒有被說服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  還想把佈景花塗黑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是模特  臉真小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是安那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  姐姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安那好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是安那  但又不是平常的她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉好小哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天5點開始  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二…二鳥君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍張照先
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一張
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了做好了  海報
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一看  真穗果然是模特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下不要弄得那麼誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難為情的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上這麼說  姿勢擺得倒是很誇張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  文化祭馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起幹活到晚上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…羅…羅密歐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好猶豫的  茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅密歐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要從窗邊將你那被迷惘束縛的心靈放飛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比任何人都要美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  千葉同學好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有那樣的台詞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我拖你後腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將徹徹底底地成為羅密歐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在正式演出中做到完美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣的話 又只會留下淒慘的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到家爸爸在練習月球漫步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你是茱麗葉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}我說佐佐啊  這個你會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}剛剛試著做過  沒成功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會徹底變成茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到的話  我會很困擾的
